Package: fastnntr
Title: Fast Rust-Based SplitsTree NeighbourNet Algorithm
Version: 0.2.5
Authors@R: 
    person("Rhys", "Newell", , "rhys.newell94@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A fast Rust implementation of the NeighbourNet algorithm
    (Bryant & Moulton, 2004) for phylogenetic analysis. It constructs an
    implicit split network from a distance matrix and returns it in a
    'networx'-compatible structure for exploratory visualisation with
    'tanggle', 'ggplot2', or 'phangorn'.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
